-- This is auto-generated code
SELECT
    TOP 100 *
    --distinct(SubscriptionName)
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK 'https://s037costmgmt.dfs.core.windows.net/usage/exports/monthly/ACMMonthlyActualCost/20240601-20240630/Extended_v3_ACMMonthlyActualCost_20240601-20240630.parquet/**',
        FORMAT = 'PARQUET'
    ) AS [result]
    where 
    SubscriptionName like 'S7%'
    OR
    SubscriptionName like 'S8%'
    OR
    SubscriptionName like 'A%'
